008,0,Personalisation
008,1,Vehicle Key,number,Range: 1-8
008,2,Gong volume,,0 - Gong volume off\n1 - Gong volume low\n2 - Gong volume medium\n3 - Gong volume high
008,3,Distance setting,,Default Value: 3\n\nRange:\n0: Distance 1\n1: Distance 2\n2: Distance 3\n3: Distance 4
008,4,Drive program,,Setting on MMI - comfort:\n\n3: Distance 1\n4: Distance 2\n4: Distance 3\n5: Distance 4\n\nSetting on MMI - dynamic:\n\n1: Distance 1\n2: Distance 2\n2: Distance 3\n3: Distance 4\n\nSetting on MMI - standard:\n\n2: Distance 1\n3: Distance 2\n3: Distance 3\n4: Distance 4\n
