200,0,Learning,
200,1,Learning condition,,Not OK - The preconditions  for adaption of the gears are not met\nOR THE VEHICLE IS FITTED WITH AN AUTOMATIC GEARBOX/MULTITRONIC.
200,2,Learned gears,,000000: The gears have not been adapted the channel 10 basic setting has been performed OR THE VEHICLE IS FITTED WITH AN AUTOMATIC GEARBOX/MULTITRONIC\n000001: 1st gear is adapted\n000011: 1st and 2nd gear have been adapted\n000111: 1st 2nd and 3rd gear have been adapted\n001111: 1st 2nd 3rd and 4th gear have been adapted\n011111: 1st 2nd 3rd. 4th and 5th gear have been adapted\n111111: All gears have been adapted
200,3,Clutch status,,Pressed: Clutch pressed (manual gearbox only)\nUnpressed: Clutch not pressed OR VEHICLE IS FITTED WITH AN AUTOMATIC GEARBOX/MULTITRONIC
