;
;
C00,Auto Dist. Reg (J428) Coding
C01,?0000: Engine type
C02,1 = 4.2l MPI with automatic gearbox 09L
C03,1 = 4.2l FSI with automatic gearbox 09L (PR - D0G/D5P/MN5)
C04,3 = 3.0l TDI with automatic gearbox 09L/manual gearbox (PR - D1D/D1T/D1V)
C05,4 = 5.2l FSI with automatic gearbox 09E/5.0l TFSI with automatic gearbox 09E (PR- xxx/xxx)
C06,5 = 2.0l TFSI with multitronic 01J/manual (PR-D2G/D5C/D1N/D2L/D6G NOT for hardware P/N 4F0-907-561)
C07,5 = 2.8l FSI with automatic gearbox 09L/multitronic 01J/manual
C08,5 = 3.0l TFSI with 09E/manual
C09,5 = 3.2l FSI with automatic gearbox 09L/multitronic 01J/manual
C10,5 = 2.7l TDI with automatic gearbox 09L/multitronic 01J/manual
C11,6 = 2.4l MPI with multitronic 01J/manual/2.0l TDI with multitronic 01J/manual (PR - D5D/MS9/D3X)
C12,x?000: Country Setting - Always 1
C13,xx?00: Body Coding
C14,1 = Standard body (Saloon/Avant)
C15,2 = Long wheelbase(for China only)
C16,3 = Light-armoured vehicle
C17,xxx?0: Country Setting 2
C18,1 = USA (mph)
C19,2 = Canada (km/h)
C20,4 = Japan (km/h)
C21,5 = Rest of the World (mph)
C22,6 = Rest of the World (km/h)
C23,xxxx?: Optional extras
C24,1 = Vehicle With Trailer Hitch
C25,8 = Vehicle Without Trailer Hitch
